{"tid":2065691,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警告眾志","createTime":"2020-06-15T18:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T01:36:07.000Z","uid":104767,"like":42,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f40634e86248ea4c4e0d84965337491419d873fe","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"如果你哋唔打算尊重右翼，請唔好宣傳自己爭取bipartisan support<br />\n<br />\n今次BBC 事件damage control 好簡單，禁止Jeffrey Ngo 以眾志名義活動<br />\n<br />\n否則視為你地同部份抗爭者割蓆"},{"pid":"7b14b4f69a556d6b4ba38459d53da2e466197432","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"眾志係英媒The Guardians 訪問同侵割蓆，話撐侵香港人係極右<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2065648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2065648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3bb2de98224ca795d2a4dce1e9ce4abfea088857","tid":2065691,"uid":38570,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:08:53.000Z","msg":"場運動一靜<br />\n泛民啲鬼性又出返哂嚟"},{"pid":"62e8b1958482cdc7e38f688065ddb1a346d40e92","tid":2065691,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:13:18.000Z","msg":"禁止Jeffrey Ngo 以眾志名義活動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e1e4ec6766cc46ca77a826244fec63139f59d4","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8kpYxn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8kpYxn.png&h=6ec03484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政客冇資格公開批評抗爭者行為<br />\n你左癌上腦匿名出post唔會有人理<br />\n你公開就代表眾志<br />\n明唔明？<br />\n如果眾志不暫停Jeffrey Ngo 事務<br />\n或Jeffrey Ngo 本人不收回言論<br />\n等於企圖與部分抗爭者割蓆<br />\n<br />\n只有外人會公開批評抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n眾志成員以上言論將被視為其無法代表手足打國際戰線嘅證據"},{"pid":"9bc8dcad5743f6f553b7790569d75a6025d1bd6c","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62e8b1958482cdc7e38f688065ddb1a346d40e92","tid":2065691,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:13:18.000Z","msg":"禁止Jeffrey Ngo 以眾志名義活動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"Damage control 真係可以好簡單"},{"pid":"5c2c4364bdcde4396335c67232d66bbd0f0447dd","tid":2065691,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40634e86248ea4c4e0d84965337491419d873fe","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"如果你哋唔打算尊重右翼，請唔好宣傳自己爭取bipartisan support<br />\n<br />\n今次BBC 事件damage control 好簡單，禁止Jeffrey Ngo 以眾志名義活動<br />\n<br />\n否則視為你地同部份抗爭者割蓆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"係一個方法"},{"pid":"69625a0c744cf717f208e2ef13957bc39c298bb7","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推到黃之鋒睇到<br />\n希望佢仍然可以進步神速"},{"pid":"1a5fd864e1b96da7556b930615b1641544ccb124","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:33:30.000Z","msg":"抗爭者係命運共同體<br />\n如果你係作為抗爭者一部分去做遊説<br />\n係不能夠以公開身分與任何抗爭行為割蓆<br />\n你有責任放下個人觀點<br />\n甚至為你所不屑嘅部分手足受外界批評<br />\n你哋就算幾不滿far right聲音<br />\n都只應該對內批評<br />\n<br />\n<strong>你哋係香港人<br />\n唔係外國政客</strong>"},{"pid":"9f07d1aa7b3b9c8c2d7b7211975259310d86f426","tid":2065691,"uid":147895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16416a506abd7e391a6928eb1ddde63baf48fbac","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"政客代表群眾爭取利益<br />\n<br />\n政棍利用群眾達成個人目的<br />\n<br />\nJeffrey Ngo 已證明自己係政棍<br />\n<br />\n希望眾志剩除嘅政客唔好俾佢攬炒"},{"pid":"abbcf734cd1c0e0ba2be6e33ae4498f3ecab8797","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:52:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"82494537aaa7db386943f7efe230264ef919361b","tid":2065691,"uid":71564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16416a506abd7e391a6928eb1ddde63baf48fbac","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"政客代表群眾爭取利益<br />\n<br />\n政棍利用群眾達成個人目的<br />\n<br />\nJeffrey Ngo 已證明自己係政棍<br />\n<br />\n希望眾志剩除嘅政客唔好俾佢攬炒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n只能希望眾志自己諗清楚<br />\n<br />\nbtw老實講呢啲問題好明顯可以有官腔啲既答案 點會落個bite屌trump<br />\n呢方面如果係打國際線就要有好既觸覺 <br />\n定係你地組織有自己考量 咁當我無講過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c853df96c309f532bd856ec3441de425bc0e03","tid":2065691,"uid":37348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"眾志好似唔屌得<br />\n五毛/鬼/小粉紅<br />\n自己揀一樣啦"},{"pid":"888300bf73b10ad6b04704c76f5dd95f97b2ce44","tid":2065691,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:20:53.000Z","msg":"撐Trump咪撐Trump<br />\n唔俾撐咩？<br />\n而家疫情最嚴重都係民主黨的州份<br />\n做政客做到要跪、好樣衰"},{"pid":"9248b4c72e0ced4256b0282bf03a02f53c16b6d3","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T20:02:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43565bd950c4923d64cdc92576ca63d1771e6b41","tid":2065691,"uid":34047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59c853df96c309f532bd856ec3441de425bc0e03","tid":2065691,"uid":37348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"眾志好似唔屌得<br />\n五毛/鬼/小粉紅<br />\n自己揀一樣啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T20:04:41.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n呢度有啲人/事/圈<br />\n就算做法有問題<br />\n你稍有質疑都會比人話搞分化/鬥黃"},{"pid":"1654d51a402b1279fb2283c0c87b82670bc891c5","tid":2065691,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"